column5: NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!!!!!!!
That sucks...  I'm usually good in the boat till Christmas at least... Mid January last year...

I'm ready for ice, bring it on!!!!  Nothing better than sitting in a warm permanent hut on an blistering cold day, listening to classic rock tunes, drinking beer or your beverage of choice, cooking up some hearty foods, and the comroderie of friends while fishing!!! What is better in life???

I'm always ready for ice season! Just today my truck asked me if it could be my ice shack again this year. I said: Truck, you bet.  Nick, hope to see you on Nip again this year. Last year was good, especially since Jay's tent didn't get swept across the lake haha.
Just today my truck asked me if it could be my ice shack again this year. I said: Truck, you bet. Now that right there is FUNNY!  funny cause it's true...

I'm always ready for ice season! Just today my truck asked me if it could be my ice shack again this year. I said: Truck, you bet.  Nick, hope to see you on Nip again this year. Last year was good, especially since Jay's tent didn't get swept across the lake haha.  For sure Chad!!  But that wasn't J's tent.  That was Lada Lada.  And man that was funny!!!    Taking a swig of bushmills, and see this nice facy tent go singing past Blair's hut!!  Poor guy!  He didn't come back the next year....  Wonder why?
oohh right, I was second guessing, thinking maybe it was Joey haha. Good times..

I was having a crappy morning today..  Until I saw THIS!!!!  Orr Lake - Nov 13.   Time to tune up the auger and sled!! Polish the Williams Lube the Reels Change the braid Etc......   Anyone else getting PUMPED!!??
That's crazy.  Just not ready for ice
ICE its only good use is making your drinks cold.......   Art
Here crappies.
Anyone else getting PUMPED!!??   Yeah, I'm getting pumped for spring
ICE its only good use is making your drinks cold.......   Art Best answer! LOL
ok I give. lets just get it over with. c,mon spring
Ahhhhhh,  The first signs of winternet!
AAAOOOHHH BABY!!
my parents place on scugog had ice for the first 50-60 feet off there shoreline. crazy
Best to embrace winter than fight it off until spring. That's why I'm heading south asap. Virginia looks better then that ice stuff.
just walk gingerly NAW, and don't jump around too much, you should be good to go (Hahaha)
To bad there's no fish in Orr lake!!
Yup I'm ready !!!
You and terry should join Jason and I on an early ice crappie session this year!
YUUUUUUPPPPPPPP and visaversa
I m packed and ready to go  running out of room in the jeep
You need to buy one of those mini buses.LMAO
I was excited to go for a grouse hunt in the snow. Two minutes north of Barrie and there's no snow.
I'm all set now bring on the ice
noooooooo not yet
I'm tired of fall, now bring on the ice.
Can't call yourself a real Canadian if you don't like winter!!!

So nobody here has learned their lesson yet??? Never say your packed and ready for ice fishing, or its almost a sure thing youll be waiting another 6 weeks. What you should say is the opposite, boats packed, time to hit soft water! Lol. I just remembered one for the superstition thread
Around here it is forecast to be 13 and rainy on Saturday. Given the last 20 years we're at least a month away from real winter.
